  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5655573/" class="title-link">无形的遗产</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5655573"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1679535-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">维舟</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-15 22:28:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5655573_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  衰落，是手工艺在面对现代化浪潮时不可避免的命运。机器大规模批量生产的商品，迟早都会逐渐取代原先手工制造的同类产品，而现代化不可逆转的推进，又会带来社会整体生活方式的剧烈变迁，从而使依赖于原先那种生活方式而存在的手艺也随之消逝——当现代人习惯于抛弃旧物的生活...

